text: The Babysitter is a 2017 American teen comedy horror movie directed by McG and written by Brian Duffield. It stars Samara Weaving, Judah Lewis, Hana Mae Lee, Robbie Amell and Bella Thorne. The movie was released by Netflix on October 13, 2017, and received mostly positive reviews from critics. A sequel, The Babysitter: Killer Queen, was released on September 10, 2020. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:2017 comedy movies Category:2017 horror movies Category:Netflix movies Category:American comedy movies Category:American horror movies Category:Movies about bullying
